{"tid":606190,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★片！印度妻被指出軌　遭丈夫綁樹下鞭100下　圍觀冷血男乘機性侵","createTime":"2018-03-26T09:44:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-26T11:42:58.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"84f27b6cf3b854f100da056b52b23c176c694b25","tid":606190,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T09:44:17.000Z","msg":"事發在本月10日，於印度北方邦布蘭德斯哈赫爾（Bulandshahr）的一條村莊， 25歲的人妻因懷疑有外遇，及與另一名男子同居，並計劃私奔，村內的長老團（Panchayati raj）決定容許她的丈夫向她鞭笞100下以作懲罰。<br />\n<br />\n該名丈夫虐打妻子的片段在網上流傳，可見妻子的雙手被吊起綁在樹上，丈夫用皮帶用力地抽打她，妻子痛得尖叫，卻無法逃走，而大群男人則圍着大樹冷眼旁觀，無人上前阻止。據了解，女子期後失去知覺，更被幾名男子帶走侵犯，最後還警告她不要報警，否則會殺了她。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">(片在 Link內最底)<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/171714/%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E5%A6%BB%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E5%87%BA%E8%BB%8C-%E9%81%AD%E4%B8%88%E5%A4%AB%E7%B6%81%E6%A8%B9%E4%B8%8B%E9%9E%AD100%E4%B8%8B-%E5%9C%8D%E8%A7%80%E5%86%B7%E8%A1%80%E7%94%B7%E4%B9%98%E6%A9%9F%E6%80%A7%E4%BE%B5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%2586%25B1%25E7%2588%2586%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E9%25A1%258C%2F171714%2F%25E5%258D%25B0%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E5%25A6%25BB%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%2587%25BA%25E8%25BB%258C-%25E9%2581%25AD%25E4%25B8%2588%25E5%25A4%25AB%25E7%25B6%2581%25E6%25A8%25B9%25E4%25B8%258B%25E9%259E%25AD100%25E4%25B8%258B-%25E5%259C%258D%25E8%25A7%2580%25E5%2586%25B7%25E8%25A1%2580%25E7%2594%25B7%25E4%25B9%2598%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%2580%25A7%25E4%25BE%25B5&d=lB94GkTWBmGCjNDwVyBISC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=3fb6da89\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/171714/%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E5%A6%BB%E